If...

18
00:02:29,899 --> 00:02:32,735
I'm sorry If you got offended by
how I jumped to conclusions like that.

19
00:02:33,361 --> 00:02:36,614
But I've never thought of you
more than a friend, so don't worry.

20
00:02:36,698 --> 00:02:37,907
What, worry?

21
00:02:38,867 --> 00:02:40,160
That's not what I meant.

22
00:02:40,243 --> 00:02:41,870
We're friends, right?

23
00:02:42,453 --> 00:02:45,290
I really think of you just as a friend.

24
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:48,293
100 percent.

25
00:02:52,088 --> 00:02:52,922
Hey.

26
00:02:54,757 --> 00:02:55,967
By any chance, do you...

27
00:02:57,677 --> 00:02:59,679
Do you have a crush on someone else?

28
00:03:04,017 --> 00:03:05,602
No, I don't have a crush on anyone.

29
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:12,984
See you tomorrow.
I'm going to go.

30
00:04:09,499 --> 00:04:10,625
Do you by any chance...

31
00:04:12,085 --> 00:04:13,753
have any feelings for me?

32
